annotationA: ADP-ribosylation factor-like protein 2; GTP-binding protein involved in protein trafficking; may modulate vesicle budding and uncoating within the Golgi apparatus
annotationB: Tubulin-binding cofactor B (TBCB) is one of the cofactors required for the assembly of functional alpha/beta-Tubulin dimers needed for microtubule assembly. TBCB is essential for microtubule-associated transport and cell polarity, but not for cell division
